title: Final Audit Report On Committee To Re-Elect Loretta Sanchez
html:
News Releases, Media Advisories

August 14, 2003

ATTENTION WIRE SERVICES, DAYBOOK EDITORS:
FINAL AUDIT REPORT ON
COMMITTEE TO RE-ELECT LORETTA SANCHEZ
The Federal Election Commission has made available the final audit report on Committee to Re-Elect Loretta Sanchez (CA 46th District). This audit covers the period of January 1, 2001 through December 31, 2002.

Contact: FEC Press Office (202) 694-1220, 999 E Street, NW
